item.title: CVE-2020-5622|2024-08-04T08:39:25.017Z -- cyber%20security%20cloud%20%2C%20inc. -- shadankun%20server%20security%20type%20%28excluding%20normal%20blocking%20method%20types%29
item.description: Shadankun Server Security Type (excluding normal blocking method types) Ver.1.5.3 and earlier allows remote attackers to cause a denial of service which may result in not being able to add newly detected attack source IP addresses as blocking targets for about 10 minutes via a specially crafted request.
